{"tid":722932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"莊閒不分(長文)","createTime":"2018-06-30T03:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T03:53:15.000Z","uid":158145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"477536dda9a23543c7cbb97d3ab8b4bc82a3e889","tid":722932,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"近日我表妹暫住我地屋企,開頭幾日都冇問題正正常常,過幾日就開始黎料。<br />\n     成日霸住個電腦煲韓劇/大陸劇,我地就叫佢讓部電腦比我地用,佢即刻發哂脾氣,話哂過門都係客,我都冇佢辦法.....<br />\n     食飯時,我阿媽煮咗一盤雞翼,預咗每人食5隻,事前都有同表妹講,點知佢食咗1x隻,我阿媽問佢點解食過量,佢就話:我中意食呀嘛,我平時喺屋企都係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"ab42dfd429ae449ddbe57973d2758f5f8d8eecd2","tid":722932,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"你表妹大唔大波先"},{"pid":"d4ee3cee9b117d9825bee02bbb9c8b4d77f36140","tid":722932,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab42dfd429ae449ddbe57973d2758f5f8d8eecd2","tid":722932,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"你表妹大唔大波先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"小6,未發育"},{"pid":"473d82a0ca858115018b3adcb13cef80d701ee25","tid":722932,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ee3cee9b117d9825bee02bbb9c8b4d77f36140","tid":722932,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab42dfd429ae449ddbe57973d2758f5f8d8eecd2","tid":722932,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"你表妹大唔大波先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:42:14.000Z","msg":"小6,未發育"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"調教由細做起"},{"pid":"5183a3ac3c394b56ceb959c6ec9369b95fa7dd8e","tid":722932,"uid":167219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"平時係屋企都係咁<br />\n即係家教唔好<br />\n解決辦法係換左d屋企人佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}